  "body": "The return value for 0 should be 0x\n\nIn addition to the 2 cases below, please review and fix any other APIs.  (The 2 cases below are eth_getBalance and eth_getTransactionCount returning 0x0 and 0 respectively.  Note, with eth_getTransactionCount the spec says the return value should be hex string https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC#eth_gettransactioncount )\n\n```\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xfd4ed114ef85d350d6d40ed3f6dc23743f8f99c4\", \"latest\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8080\n{\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n    \"result\": \"0x0\"\n}%                                  \n```\n\n```\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionCount\",\"params\":[\"0x9dc2299a76b68b7ffa9e3ba0fd8cd7646d21d400\",\"pending\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8080\n{\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n    \"result\": 0\n}%\n```\n",
